Package: SECDataViewer
Title: SEC Data Viewer and Analyzer
Version: 1.0.0
Description: A Shiny application and API for exploring SEC filings, visualizing financial data, and performing sentiment analysis on 10-K reports using the Loughran-McDonald dictionary.
